in the essays found in the 12 &amp; 12. Nobody can stay sober off of the
generalizations found in the written steps themselves.

<p>
<font color="blue">
I quoted the 12 Steps directly from the <i>Big Book</i>, not from pamphlets or wallet cards. See
<a href="orange-interpreted.html" target="_blank">The Twelve Steps Interpreted</a>.
<p>
And what is this line??!!
<p>
<blockquote> 
<font color="black" face="Lucida,Utopia bold,Utopia,Helvetica,Charter,Arial,sans-serif,Sans Serif,New Century Schoolbook">
&quot;Nobody can stay sober off of the generalizations found in the written steps themselves.&quot;<br>
</font>
</blockquote>
<p>
