The Twelve Steps, as written in the <i>Big Book</i>, are vague generalizations that don't work
to get people sober?
A lot of other Steppers will disagree with you about that.
<p>
I suppose you need a sponsor to tell you
&quot;<a href="orange-cult_q0.html#cq_cult_speak" target="_blank&quot;">what the words
really mean</a>&quot;, right?
</font>
<p>
