<li> &quot;Strength in powerlessness.&quot;<br>
<li> &quot;I pray to God every day that I never get the idea that I can run my own life.&quot;<br>
<li> &quot;I know I'm in trouble when I start thinking I can run my own life.&quot;<br>
</ol>

</font>
